description: FINAL HOMES REMAINING — Unbeatable New Pricing for a Limited Time! Welcome to ARCHER SULLIVAN, carefully crafted with living and growing in mind. This limited collection of move in ready, 3 bedroom residences features up to 1650+ square feet with expansive rooftop decks, air conditioning and double-car garages. Architecturally inspired and elevated by exceptional design. Interior materials and finishings all hand selected by the Award Winning team at Tali+Roche Interior Design. Nestled in the heart of Surrey’s Sullivan neighbourhood - ARCHER brought to life by OVI Homes + Kennedy Development, a new standard of living in Surrey.
